  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 200°C.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chopped peanuts, parsley, and cilantro to the bowl and mix well.",
    "Add the chicken breast to the bowl and mix until well coated with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated chicken, bell peppers, onion, and garlic onto the skewers.",
    "Place the skewers on the preheated grill and cook for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "Brush the skewers with olive oil and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Remove the skewers from the grill and let them rest for 5 minutes.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
